    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_23_18395-18421",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "18395-18421",
      "markText": "不过，这可能是我的错觉。这一切仿佛在我眼前浮掠过去。",
      "totalCount": 5004,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=18395&rangeEnd=18421",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=18395&rangeEnd=18421"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_4_8797-8870",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8797-8870",
      "markText": "这一切都得归功于坚持不懈的努力，归功于有自知之明，宁可把自己看得渺小，永远力戒骄傲，力戒过早的自满，力戒懒惰，因为懒惰是这种自满情绪的必然结果。”",
      "totalCount": 2268,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8797&rangeEnd=8870",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8797&rangeEnd=8870"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_16_18006-18032",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "18006-18032",
      "markText": "“您一只鞋的鞋带松开了，”她对我说，“我来帮您系。”",
      "totalCount": 2250,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=18006&rangeEnd=18032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=18006&rangeEnd=18032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_4_8134-8195",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8134-8195",
      "markText": "说到底，甚至他的才也许一开始就没有什么了不起，而多的是盲目和不切实际的自信、浅薄的自负以及不断幻想自己是盖世奇才的白日梦。",
      "totalCount": 2070,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8134&rangeEnd=8195",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8134&rangeEnd=8195"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_17_8585-8614",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "8585-8614",
      "markText": "“我记得以前你夜里是怎样吻我的！”她说时脸红得像朵罂粟花。",
      "totalCount": 1980,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=8585&rangeEnd=8614",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=8585&rangeEnd=8614"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_17_16136-16182",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "16136-16182",
      "markText": "我们最后一次互相拥抱，随后小郡主便消失了——她这一次去了很久很久。直到八年以后我们才得重逢！",
      "totalCount": 1872,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=16136&rangeEnd=16182",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=16136&rangeEnd=16182"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_8_5840-5927",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5840-5927",
      "markText": "末了，他甚至还补充几句，要我心疼妈妈，因为妈妈身体很不好，怪可怜的，她一个人为我们大家干活。我听着心里非常害怕，浑身发抖，眼泪忍不住要掉下来。我震惊得话也说不出，动也动不了。",
      "totalCount": 1853,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5840&rangeEnd=5927",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5840&rangeEnd=5927"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_5_2979-3058",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2979-3058",
      "markText": "他的眼睛里燃烧起少有的勇气和希望。不久，这种高尚的勇气转为自负，接着又变成平时那份狂妄，最后，当Б快要结束这番规劝的时候，叶菲莫夫已经心不在焉，听得不耐烦了。",
      "totalCount": 1700,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2979&rangeEnd=3058",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2979&rangeEnd=3058"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098531_17_12340-12388",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "12340-12388",
      "markText": "“难道不是吗？现在，你爱把我怎么样就怎么样！折磨我，拧我吧！请你拧我一把！我的宝贝，拧我一把！”",
      "totalCount": 1568,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098531&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=12340&rangeEnd=12388",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0932800813ab8cfdg0111df?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=12340&rangeEnd=12388"
    },
    {
